@page "/About"

<PageTitle>About us</PageTitle>

<main>
    <section id="mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is simple: to provide a seamless and enjoyable experience for book enthusiasts to buy and sell used books. We believe in the power of storytelling and the value of sharing knowledge, and we're committed to making it easier for books to find new homes and readers to find their next literary adventure.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="what-sets-us-apart">
        <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Diverse Selection:</strong> With a wide range of genres, from classics to contemporary fiction, non-fiction to graphic novels, we offer something for every reader's taste.</li>
            <li><strong>User-Friendly Interface:</strong> Our website is designed with simplicity and convenience in mind. Easily browse listings, connect with sellers, and complete transactions hassle-free.</li>
            <li><strong>Community Engagement:</strong> We're more than just a marketplace; we're a community of book lovers. Engage with fellow readers, share recommendations, and connect over your mutual love for books.</li>
            <li><strong>Seller Support:</strong> We provide sellers with the tools and resources they need to list their books efficiently and effectively. From pricing guidance to shipping assistance, we're here to help you every step of the way.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="how-it-works">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Selling your used books on <strong>[book_store_name]</strong> is as easy as 1-2-3:</p>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>List Your Books:</strong> Create a free account, upload photos and descriptions of your books, and set your price.</li>
            <li><strong>Connect with Buyers:</strong> Engage with potential buyers through linked messaging systems to negotiate terms and finalize the sale.</li>
            <li><strong>Ship and Get Paid:</strong> Once you've reached an agreement, package your books securely and ship them to the buyer. Once they receive their purchase, you'll receive payment.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>Buying books is just as simple:</p>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Browse Listings:</strong> Explore our diverse selection of used books by genre, author, or keyword.</li>
            <li><strong>Contact Sellers:</strong> Reach out to sellers directly through linked messaging systems to ask questions or negotiate prices.</li>
            <li><strong>Purchase and Enjoy:</strong> Once you've found the perfect book, complete your purchase securely through our platform and await your new literary treasure.</li>
        </ol>
    </section>
    <section id="join-our-community">
        <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
        <p>Ready to embark on your next reading journey? Join the <strong>[book_store_name]</strong> community today! Whether you're looking to sell your used books or expand your personal library, we're here to help you every step of the way. Happy reading!</p>
    </section>
</main>

